        <abstract> 
<p>Sends first copy of new [6th] edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Expenses have been much higher than estimated because of extensive revisions. 3000 copies retailing at 6s would yield only £100 profit. Suggests fixing price at 7s 6d.</p> 
        </abstract>
